<title>TBox中间件服务架构</title>
<style>
body{font-family:"Microsoft YaHei","SimSun",sans-serif;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:1.6;color:#333;margin:60px 72px}
@page{size:A4;margin:2.54cm 3.18cm 2.54cm 3.18cm}
h1,h2,h3,h4{font-family:"Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif}
